<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>H38-T007 Cleanup Index</title>
<style>
  body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;margin:14px;background:#fff;color:#111827}
  table{border-collapse:collapse;width:1240px;table-layout:fixed}
  th,td{border:1px solid #b7c3d0;padding:8px 10px;vertical-align:top;white-space:normal;word-wrap:break-word;line-height:1.35;mso-number-format:"\@"}
  th{background:#dbeafe;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a}.title{background:#1f2937;color:#fff;font-size:16pt;text-align:left;padding:12px}.sub{background:#f8fafc;color:#475569;font-style:italic}.narrow{text-align:center}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<table>
<colgroup><col style="width:140px"><col style="width:205px"><col style="width:185px"><col style="width:120px"><col style="width:230px"><col style="width:100px"><col style="width:260px"></colgroup>
<tr><th class="title" colspan="7">Highway 38 Solutions - H38-T007 Cleanup Index Sample</th></tr>
<tr><td class="sub" colspan="7">Use this index to sort receipts, photos, screenshots, notes, and archive files into an action-ready structure.</td></tr>
<tr><th>File Group</th><th>Example Item</th><th>New Folder</th><th>Status</th><th>Action Needed</th><th>Priority</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
<tr><td>Receipt</td><td>hardware-store-receipt</td><td>01 Receipts</td><td class="narrow">Sorted</td><td>Enter amount</td><td class="narrow">Medium</td><td>Rename with date and vendor.</td></tr>
<tr><td>Photo</td><td>garage-before-photo</td><td>02 Proof Photos</td><td class="narrow">Sorted</td><td>Keep original</td><td class="narrow">High</td><td>Use for customer packet.</td></tr>
<tr><td>Screenshot</td><td>product-link</td><td>03 Reference</td><td class="narrow">Sorted</td><td>Check if still needed</td><td class="narrow">Low</td><td>Reference only, not proof.</td></tr>
<tr><td>Note</td><td>call-notes</td><td>04 Action Needed</td><td class="narrow">Open</td><td>Reply or decide</td><td class="narrow">High</td><td>Needs owner review.</td></tr>
<tr><td>Old file</td><td>duplicate-photo</td><td>99 Archive</td><td class="narrow">Archive</td><td>None</td><td class="narrow">Low</td><td>Do not delete until confirmed.</td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
